988
00:30:11,119 --> 00:30:13,799
[SPEAKER_01] I mi ti možeš reći što se dogodilo?

989
00:30:13,799 --> 00:30:15,039
[SPEAKER_01] Kak je ona odreagirala?

990
00:30:15,039 --> 00:30:16,420
[SPEAKER_00] Pa dobro.

991
00:30:16,599 --> 00:30:19,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je mogla vjerovati da si ti zapravo to odjedno.

992
00:30:19,859 --> 00:30:20,519
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

993
00:30:20,519 --> 00:30:23,299
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je ti je meni napisala,

994
00:30:23,299 --> 00:30:24,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ivana,

995
00:30:24,420 --> 00:30:26,759
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da si krivoj osobi poslala poruku.

996
00:30:26,759 --> 00:30:27,319
[SPEAKER_01] Kao pogrej.

997
00:30:27,319 --> 00:30:28,660
[SPEAKER_01] Rekao, ne, ne, tebi sam.

998
00:30:28,660 --> 00:30:31,079
[SPEAKER_01] Jer nju je valjno osupno ta sva ljubav.

999
00:30:31,079 --> 00:30:33,740
[SPEAKER_01] I ona nije mogla vjerovati da sam ja poslala tu poruku.

1000
00:30:33,740 --> 00:30:36,619
[SPEAKER_01] I ja sam odlučila biti drugačija prema njoj.

1001
00:30:36,619 --> 00:30:38,400
[SPEAKER_01] I naš odnos se počeo mijenjati.

1002
00:30:38,400 --> 00:30:40,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ona sam to opisala čak i u knjizi,

1003
00:30:40,019 --> 00:30:40,680
[SPEAKER_01] jer je onda sam rekla,

1004
00:30:40,680 --> 00:30:42,240
[SPEAKER_01] ako jednog dana prečete ovu knjigu,

1005
00:30:42,319 --> 00:30:44,279
[SPEAKER_01] da ću skužiti kako smo postale prijateljice.

1006
00:30:44,279 --> 00:30:46,680
[SPEAKER_01] Toliko dobro da sam ja nju htjela da bude kuma,

1007
00:30:46,680 --> 00:30:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] jednom od moje djece.

1008
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:50,740
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, onda je ona tišla van Hrvatske i tako.

1009
00:30:50,799 --> 00:30:53,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ali evo, sve se može kad se hoće,

1010
00:30:53,619 --> 00:30:54,880
[SPEAKER_01] pa tako i to opraštanje,

1011
00:30:54,880 --> 00:30:57,559
[SPEAKER_01] koje evo, dosta ljudi to krivo poimlje,

1012
00:30:57,559 --> 00:30:59,700
[SPEAKER_01] misle da ako oni opraštaju,

1013
00:30:59,700 --> 00:31:01,660
[SPEAKER_01] da oni u stvari daju za pravo

1014
00:31:01,660 --> 00:31:03,880
[SPEAKER_01] toj drugoj osobi koja ih je ranila,

1015
00:31:03,880 --> 00:31:05,819
[SPEAKER_01] da ono, aha, sad sam ja tu,

1016
00:31:05,819 --> 00:31:07,500
[SPEAKER_01] kao, ja ću sad pogaziti sebe,

1017
00:31:07,500 --> 00:31:09,119
[SPEAKER_01] svoj ego, ono,

1018
00:31:09,119 --> 00:31:10,839
[SPEAKER_01] mene je osoba, ali kao,

1019
00:31:10,839 --> 00:31:13,460
[SPEAKER_01] to je nepravedno i sad bi ja trebao oprašnati.

1020
00:31:13,460 --> 00:31:15,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, opraštamo zbog sebe.

1021
00:31:15,039 --> 00:31:17,759
[SPEAKER_01] Jer smo mi ranjeni tuđom povredom

1022
00:31:17,759 --> 00:31:20,680
[SPEAKER_01] i mi sebe spašavamo, nećući spašavamo,

1023
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:24,359
[SPEAKER_01] ali omogućavamo život dalje opraštanjem.

1024
00:31:24,359 --> 00:31:26,819
[SPEAKER_01] To je različito od onoga kako vele pomirenje.

1025
00:31:26,819 --> 00:31:29,720
[SPEAKER_01] Do pomirenja dolazi kada druga osoba shvati,

1026
00:31:29,720 --> 00:31:32,019
[SPEAKER_01] kad se pokaje i kad želi se pomiriti.

1027
00:31:32,019 --> 00:31:34,460
[SPEAKER_01] E onda tu možemo raditi na nekom odnosu.

1028
00:31:34,460 --> 00:31:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ako mene netko povrijedi,

1029
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:39,880
[SPEAKER_01] to recimo evo sad držim neke radionice za djecu i tako

1030
00:31:39,880 --> 00:31:41,359
[SPEAKER_01] i bitno mi je to opraštanje

1031
00:31:41,359 --> 00:31:44,420
[SPEAKER_01] i ovaj, i onda kažem tu jednu situaciju

1032
00:31:44,420 --> 00:31:46,940
[SPEAKER_01] koju sam u stvari naučila od jedne časne sestre

1033
00:31:46,940 --> 00:31:48,160
[SPEAKER_01] koju sam došla slušat

1034
00:31:48,160 --> 00:31:50,440
[SPEAKER_01] u trenutku kad nisam htjela ništa slušat.

1035
00:31:50,440 --> 00:31:52,539
[SPEAKER_01] Jer upravo me pet minuta prije toga

1036
00:31:52,539 --> 00:31:54,299
[SPEAKER_01] povrijedila jedna osoba koja sam

1037
00:31:54,299 --> 00:31:56,660
[SPEAKER_01] ono, i srce, dušu, tijelo, sve sam joj dala.

1038
00:31:56,660 --> 00:31:58,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, baš sam bila onak dobar mentor

1039
00:31:58,559 --> 00:32:00,059
[SPEAKER_01] i strpljiv i sve.

1040
00:32:00,059 --> 00:32:01,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je mene tako izvrijeđala.

1041
00:32:01,720 --> 00:32:03,779
[SPEAKER_01] Da ne dajem joj vrijeme, da se ne trudimo oko nje.

1042
00:32:03,779 --> 00:32:05,140
[SPEAKER_01] I onda mi još spustila slušalicu.

1043
00:32:05,140 --> 00:32:06,759
[SPEAKER_01] Inak mislim si, koje predavanje?

1044
00:32:06,759 --> 00:32:08,319
[SPEAKER_01] Nije koje predavanje me sad ne interesira.

1045
00:32:08,319 --> 00:32:10,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ja idem doma, idem žalit sam u sebe.

1046
00:32:10,420 --> 00:32:10,940
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

1047
00:32:10,940 --> 00:32:11,700
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ništa.

1048
00:32:11,700 --> 00:32:12,859
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam već bila parkirana,

1049
00:32:12,859 --> 00:32:14,279
[SPEAKER_01] ulazila sam u tu dvoranu

1050
00:32:14,279 --> 00:32:15,539
[SPEAKER_01] i ta časna sestra je...

1051
00:32:15,539 --> 00:32:16,599
[SPEAKER_01] U stvari, ja sam htjela vidjeti

1052
00:32:16,599 --> 00:32:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] časnu sestru na skejtu.

1053
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:19,119
[SPEAKER_01] Jer to je bila reklama.

1054
00:32:19,119 --> 00:32:20,359
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, časna na skejtu.

1055
00:32:20,359 --> 00:32:22,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam, ta fisto nisam već bila obraćena,

1056
00:32:22,380 --> 00:32:23,660
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam htjela idući vidjeti cirkus.

1057
00:32:24,539 --> 00:32:26,400
[SPEAKER_01] I u stvari, ona je pričala o praštanju.

1058
00:32:26,400 --> 00:32:28,400
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, prva tema koja se ona dotakla,

1059
00:32:28,400 --> 00:32:29,980
[SPEAKER_01] ona je ovako nacrtala jedno srce

1060
00:32:29,980 --> 00:32:31,759
[SPEAKER_01] i probola ga je olovkom.

1061
00:32:31,759 --> 00:32:34,180
[SPEAKER_01] I rekla je, kada vas netko povrijedi,

1062
00:32:34,180 --> 00:32:37,180
[SPEAKER_01] pokušajte njihovo srce vidjeti,

1063
00:32:37,180 --> 00:32:39,279
[SPEAKER_01] ne njih kao zle ovakve, onakve,

1064
00:32:39,279 --> 00:32:40,339
[SPEAKER_01] koje su vam htjeli napakostiti,

1065
00:32:40,339 --> 00:32:41,839
[SPEAKER_01] nego pogledajte njihovo srce

1066
00:32:41,839 --> 00:32:43,640
[SPEAKER_01] koje je probodeno sa šiljcima.

1067
00:32:43,640 --> 00:32:46,940
[SPEAKER_01] Jer oni su isto na neki način ranjeni.

1068
00:32:46,940 --> 00:32:49,240
[SPEAKER_01] I oni bi možda htjeli sa srcem prići vam,

1069
00:32:49,240 --> 00:32:51,559
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne mogu jer ih nešto muči.

1070
00:32:51,640 --> 00:32:53,039
[SPEAKER_01] I onda vam, nažalost, pristupi.

1071
00:32:53,039 --> 00:32:54,579
[SPEAKER_01] Kad je ona to tako jednostavno objasnila,

1072
00:32:54,579 --> 00:32:58,799
[SPEAKER_01] te sekunde sam ja tu djevojku vidjela ranjenu

1073
00:32:58,799 --> 00:33:01,039
[SPEAKER_01] sa tim njenim srcem i njenim šiljcima.

1074
00:33:01,039 --> 00:33:04,539
[SPEAKER_01] I onak, ajme, pa ne mogu joj ništa zamjerati.

1075
00:33:04,539 --> 00:33:05,579
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ona je isto ranjena.

1076
00:33:05,579 --> 00:33:08,460
[SPEAKER_01] I te sekunde ja sam imala totalno drugi gard

1077
00:33:08,460 --> 00:33:09,519
[SPEAKER_01] prema njoj.

1078
00:33:09,519 --> 00:33:11,740
[SPEAKER_01] I to je bilo jedno suosjećanje.

1079
00:33:11,740 --> 00:33:13,900
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mislim da osoba bez obzira

1080
00:33:13,900 --> 00:33:15,960
[SPEAKER_01] kakvu traumu, naravno, ja nisam doživjela,

1081
00:33:15,960 --> 00:33:19,299
[SPEAKER_01] neću reći ne znam kako velike traume u životu.

1082
00:33:19,299 --> 00:33:21,059
[SPEAKER_01] I evo, hvala dragom Bogu da nisam

1083
00:33:21,640 --> 00:33:23,940
[SPEAKER_01] znao sam, eto, bila ranjena na druge neke načine.

1084
00:33:23,940 --> 00:33:26,680
[SPEAKER_01] Kroz laž, kroz zabluda i sve ostalo.

1085
00:33:26,680 --> 00:33:29,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ako čovjek ne spozna,

1086
00:33:29,559 --> 00:33:32,460
[SPEAKER_01] znači to je ono što to je djeci u stvari kaže.

1087
00:33:32,460 --> 00:33:34,460
[SPEAKER_01] Me rekao, gledaj, kako glavni,

1088
00:33:34,460 --> 00:33:38,039
[SPEAKER_01] kako super junak u filmu rješava

1089
00:33:38,039 --> 00:33:39,680
[SPEAKER_01] kad ga neko povrijedi.

1090
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jel on hoda ostatak filma i kuka,

1091
00:33:42,000 --> 00:33:45,480
[SPEAKER_01] glej kak me povrijedio, glej kak me on je tamo zločesti ranio.

1092
00:33:45,480 --> 00:33:46,819
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, on to ne radi.

1093
00:33:46,819 --> 00:33:50,359
[SPEAKER_01] On to, ne znam da li je to sad neki predmet ili nešto,

1094
00:33:50,599 --> 00:33:51,599
[SPEAKER_01] on ga iščupa,

1095
00:33:51,599 --> 00:33:54,460
[SPEAKER_01] poveže ranu da može ići spasiti grad.

1096
00:33:54,460 --> 00:33:56,920
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, on ne kuka.

1097
00:33:56,920 --> 00:34:00,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mi svi, mi smo svi super junaciji u svojim životima.

1098
00:34:00,420 --> 00:34:02,019
[SPEAKER_01] I trebali bi se tako ponašati.

1099
00:34:02,019 --> 00:34:03,339
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mi idemo, joj, gledaj mene,

1100
00:34:03,339 --> 00:34:04,500
[SPEAKER_01] glej kak sam ja žrtva,

1101
00:34:04,500 --> 00:34:06,039
[SPEAKER_01] glej kak je meni teško,

1102
00:34:06,039 --> 00:34:07,200
[SPEAKER_01] ja ne umanjujem,

1103
00:34:07,200 --> 00:34:09,519
[SPEAKER_01] nić je, nić je rane.

1104
00:34:10,000 --> 00:34:12,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ali moramo spoznati da opraštanjem,

1105
00:34:12,360 --> 00:34:14,800
[SPEAKER_01] mi vadimo taj šiljak iz svog srca,

1106
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:15,440
[SPEAKER_01] taj otrov,

1107
00:34:15,440 --> 00:34:16,900
[SPEAKER_01] vadimo van,

1108
00:34:16,900 --> 00:34:20,320
[SPEAKER_01] da bi Bog mogao nas zacijeliti.

1109
00:34:20,320 --> 00:34:21,360
[SPEAKER_01] Puno ljudi kaže,

1110
00:34:21,360 --> 00:34:22,420
[SPEAKER_01] da, da, ja se molim,

1111
00:34:22,420 --> 00:34:23,860
[SPEAKER_01] sakramentalno živim,

1112
00:34:23,860 --> 00:34:25,059
[SPEAKER_01] ali evo, ne mogu uzdraviti,

1113
00:34:25,059 --> 00:34:26,199
[SPEAKER_01] ne mogu ovo, ne mogu ono.

1114
00:34:26,199 --> 00:34:29,139
[SPEAKER_01] I onda dođemo do toga da ta osoba ne može oprostiti.

1115
00:34:29,860 --> 00:34:31,519
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, pričala si sad oprost o drugima,

1116
00:34:31,519 --> 00:34:33,500
[SPEAKER_00] a što je oprost pre samom sebi?

1117
00:34:33,500 --> 00:34:34,300
[SPEAKER_01] Sebi, da.

1118
00:34:34,300 --> 00:34:36,900
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, baš to, evo,

1119
00:34:36,900 --> 00:34:38,179
[SPEAKER_01] to već u srednjoj školi,

1120
00:34:38,179 --> 00:34:39,480
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam vidjela sebe,

1121
00:34:39,480 --> 00:34:40,820
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam shvatila da moram,

1122
00:34:40,820 --> 00:34:43,519
[SPEAKER_01] da ja moram neke stvari u sebi promijeniti.

1123
00:34:43,519 --> 00:34:44,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam mogla isto,

1124
00:34:44,420 --> 00:34:45,699
[SPEAKER_01] vi, kada vidiš ove mi je ovako,

1125
00:34:45,699 --> 00:34:46,360
[SPEAKER_01] ove mi je ovako,

1126
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:49,099
[SPEAKER_01] ali jednostavno kad čovjek spozna tko je,

1127
00:34:49,099 --> 00:34:50,960
[SPEAKER_01] znači ako ja spoznam danas,

1128
00:34:50,960 --> 00:34:52,860
[SPEAKER_01] da sam ja Božje dijete

1129
00:34:52,860 --> 00:34:55,480
[SPEAKER_01] i da mi je Bog toliko je omogućio

1130
00:34:55,480 --> 00:34:56,340
[SPEAKER_01] i toliko dao,

1131
00:34:56,420 --> 00:34:59,539
[SPEAKER_01] a ja spriječavam svojim odlukama,

1132
00:34:59,539 --> 00:35:02,880
[SPEAKER_01] svojom ustrajnošću

1133
00:35:02,880 --> 00:35:05,619
[SPEAKER_01] i na tom spriječavam milosti

1134
00:35:05,619 --> 00:35:07,380
[SPEAKER_01] koje mogu dobiti od dragog Boga.

1135
00:35:07,380 --> 00:35:09,920
[SPEAKER_01] Onda ponašam se veoma nerazumno

1136
00:35:09,920 --> 00:35:11,099
[SPEAKER_01] i veoma bedasto.

1137
00:35:11,099 --> 00:35:15,320
[SPEAKER_01] I prije sam to gledala na emotivnoj razini

1138
00:35:15,320 --> 00:35:17,019
[SPEAKER_01] u stilu, ha, mene niko ne razumije,

1139
00:35:17,019 --> 00:35:17,800
[SPEAKER_01] meni je teško,

1140
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:20,119
[SPEAKER_01] meni je, ja sam imala takav nadimak,

1141
00:35:20,119 --> 00:35:21,119
[SPEAKER_01] ne želim ga ovdje reći,

1142
00:35:21,119 --> 00:35:22,639
[SPEAKER_01] jer znam da bi svi umrli od smijeha,

1143
00:35:22,639 --> 00:35:24,679
[SPEAKER_01] ali taj nadimak je odrežavao

1144
00:35:24,679 --> 00:35:27,619
[SPEAKER_01] kako sam se ja većinu vremena osjećala.

1145
00:35:27,619 --> 00:35:28,980
[SPEAKER_01] Osjećala sam se kiselo,

1146
00:35:28,980 --> 00:35:31,019
[SPEAKER_01] osjećala sam se nevoljeno,

1147
00:35:31,019 --> 00:35:32,860
[SPEAKER_01] jer je mene jedna riječ tuža

1148
00:35:32,860 --> 00:35:34,019
[SPEAKER_01] mogla povrijediti.

1149
00:35:34,019 --> 00:35:36,179
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ja sam i sebe onda povrijeđivala

1150
00:35:36,179 --> 00:35:39,079
[SPEAKER_01] ustrajući u tome da ja sebe vidim

1151
00:35:39,079 --> 00:35:40,139
[SPEAKER_01] kao žrtvu.

1152
00:35:40,139 --> 00:35:41,840
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kad sam ja vidjela

1153
00:35:41,840 --> 00:35:43,900
[SPEAKER_01] što sam sebi sve napravila

1154
00:35:43,900 --> 00:35:45,539
[SPEAKER_01] kroz ovo, kroz ovo, kroz ovo,

1155
00:35:45,539 --> 00:35:47,960
[SPEAKER_01] bojme čovjek mora sjesti sam sa sobom.

1156
00:35:47,960 --> 00:35:50,199
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto ostavimo u stanju te žrtve?

1157
00:35:50,199 --> 00:35:52,179
[SPEAKER_01] Pa zato što je to lakše.

1158
00:35:53,059 --> 00:35:54,559
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, iskreno moram reći lakše,

1159
00:35:54,559 --> 00:35:57,039
[SPEAKER_01] ali upoznala sam i na svom primjeru,

1160
00:35:57,039 --> 00:35:59,400
[SPEAKER_01] lakše mi je ukriviti drugoga.

1161
00:35:59,400 --> 00:36:01,119
[SPEAKER_01] Pa mislim, Adam i Eva su to napravili.

1162
00:36:01,119 --> 00:36:02,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ako su oni to napravili,

1163
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:05,099
[SPEAKER_01] naravno, to je u našim genima ću reći

1164
00:36:05,099 --> 00:36:06,639
[SPEAKER_01] i protiv toga se moramo boriti.

1165
00:36:06,639 --> 00:36:09,039
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mi bi danas živjeli u raju

1166
00:36:09,039 --> 00:36:10,579
[SPEAKER_01] da su samo Adam i Eva rekli

1167
00:36:10,579 --> 00:36:12,739
[SPEAKER_01] sorry, fakat sam pogriješio.

1168
00:36:12,739 --> 00:36:14,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, ne.

1169
00:36:14,019 --> 00:36:16,599
[SPEAKER_01] Rađuću prstom upriti u drugoga.

1170
00:36:16,599 --> 00:36:18,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ako mi gledamo sebe,

1171
00:36:18,739 --> 00:36:20,719
[SPEAKER_01] onda ćemo vidjeti puno manjkavosti.

1172
00:36:20,719 --> 00:36:22,380
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, meni nije bilo ugodno.

1173
00:36:22,380 --> 00:36:24,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne bi nikad pustila taj film

1174
00:36:24,079 --> 00:36:25,880
[SPEAKER_01] da ja vidim kak sam ja povrijedila drugoga.

1175
00:36:25,880 --> 00:36:27,400
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je to bilo pušteno.

1176
00:36:27,400 --> 00:36:28,800
